import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import { Provider } from 'react-redux'
import { store } from './store'

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'))
root.render(
    //<React.StrictMode>
    <Provider store={store}>
        <App />
    </Provider>
    //</React.StrictMode>
)
